    <sect3 role="installation">
      <title>Instalao de Pytz</title>

      <para>
        Build the module:
      </para>

<screen><userinput>pip3 wheel -w dist --no-build-isolation --no-deps $PWD</userinput></screen>

      <para>
        Agora, como o(a) usurio(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
      </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>pip3 install --no-index --find-links dist --no-cache-dir --no-user pytz</userinput></screen>

      <para>
        To test the installation, run <command>pytest</command>. A few warnings are
issued.
      </para>

    </sect3>

